{
  "stem": "22174.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] After the Crystal Night, the-- our landlord, who had made an agreement with my father to open up a big store, he cancelled the lease for our apartment.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents had to move out [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and into-- into one room with another Jewish couple-- a-- a couple where the husband was a Russian Jew that was a prisoner of war in Germany and, had, after the war, remained in Germany and married a non-Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he gave one room to my-- to my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that house, my father died a year after-- a little over a year after he was released from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, after that, my mother was forced, again, to move out there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I imagine, because she was left alone, that she was not allowed to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to live in a room like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, she was forced again, but not by the people who owned the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they were-- he was Jewish, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But for some reason, she had to-- she was forced, again, to move out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she moved into a dingy-- dingy basement apartment-- not apartment, into a room, basement room of a house that belonged to a-- a Jewish shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and there-- there she lived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and-- there was the president of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He adored my mother, always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after my father had died, they moved together in that-- in that room, in the basement room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from then on, I-- I didn't get any more letters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes, I did get letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because, from 1938 to '39, I still get postcards.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
